projects.title: Sync & Share file storage solution
projects.description:
Easy-to-use, enterprise-grade file sync and share solution that gives the access to all users files on all users devices and content repositories such as Network Shares and SharePoint. By combining highly secure solution with a rich mobile, web and desktop experience, user gets to collaborate inside and outside him organization easily. All while giving IT professionals the security, manageability, and control they need.

Features include: 

- Upload photos, videos, documents, or any other files directly from your device to any app folder 
- Share files (All Editions) with optional password protection and restrict recipients using Secure Shared Links (Business and Enterprise Editions only)
- Mark folders and files as “favorites” to gain offline access via the industry’s only mobile “push” synchronization
- Natively create, edit, and annotate Microsoft Office files and sync them back to all devices
- Secure workflows via integrations with AirWatch & MobileIron MDM
- and more...

projects.title: Home Care
projects.description:
Search for home care agencies, nursing agencies, local authorities, care associations, care suppliers on the leading UK Care Homes app. 
We have combined all the excellent content from the homecare.co.uk website with the unrivalled functionality of the iPad. 
The Home Care app has been designed with the easy to use but also powerful searches. You can search by Category, by Current Location, by Location, by Postcode and by Name. 
The app also allows you to filter your search results by Classification (eg Live in Carer or Elderly Home Care). 
The search results are displayed in either list format or on map. You can use the Saved Feature to save entries you are interested in and you can use the Recent Feature to view all entries you have recently viewed. 
The Home Care app includes over 10,000 entries, focusing on all UK registered home care and nursing agencies, local authorities and the major care associations and suppliers.

projects.title: Britain’s Finest
projects.description:
Search for the very best accommodation, things to do and places to eat in the UK with the Britain’s Finest app. 
We have combined all the excellent content from the britainsfinest.co.uk website with the unrivalled functionality of the iPad. 
The Britain’s Finest app has been designed for ease of use but it also features powerful searches. You can search by Category, by Current Location, by Location, by Postcode and by Name. 
The app also allows you to filter your search results by Classification (eg Dog Friendly Hotels), by Facility (eg Hotels with Spas) and by Special Offers (eg. we feature hundreds of fantastic deals from luxury hotels). 
The search results are displayed in either list format or on map. You can use the Saved Feature to save entries you are interested in (allowing you to create the perfect weekend trip!) and you can use the Recent Feature to view all entries you have recently viewed. 
The Britain’s Finest app includes over 4,000 entries and 10,000 photos, focusing on the leading independent Luxury Hotels, Small Hotels & Inns, Bed & Breakfasts, Self Catering Properties, Attractions & Activities, Museums & Art Galleries, Historic Houses, Gardens, Spas, Golf Courses and Restaurants & Gastro Pubs. 
All of the these entries have been handpicked by our dedicated team of inspectors, journalists, researchers and travel enthusiasts to ensure that we feature the best of what Britain has to offer. 
Each entry has been carefully researched and includes 3 photos, 150 word description, special offers, accreditation information, price information, opening hours, contact via email, telephone numbers, link to website and a local mapping info.
